# UI 组件开发规范

## 组件分类

### @mg/ui（通用组件，7 类）

| 类别 | 路径 | 示例 |
|------|------|------|
| general | `components/general/` | Button, Badge, Link, Toggle, Separator, Icon, Typography |
| layout | `components/layout/` | Container, Grid, Stack, AspectRatio, ScrollArea |
| form | `components/form/` | Input, Select, Checkbox, Switch, Slider, DatePicker, Combobox |
| data-display | `components/data-display/` | Table, Card, Accordion, Avatar, Tag, Skeleton, Empty |
| feedback | `components/feedback/` | Alert, AlertDialog, Toast, Progress, Spinner, Meter |
| navigation | `components/navigation/` | Tabs, Breadcrumb, Pagination, Menu, NavigationMenu, Steps |
| overlay | `components/overlay/` | Dialog, Drawer, Sheet, Popover, Tooltip, DropdownMenu, ContextMenu |

### @mg/ui-commerce（电商组件，5 类）

| 类别 | 路径 | 示例 |
|------|------|------|
| product | `components/product/` | ProductCard, ProductGallery, SkuSelector, QuantityStepper |
| price | `components/price/` | PriceDisplay, PriceRange, CouponTag |
| cart | `components/cart/` | CartItem, CartSummary, CartDrawer |
| order | `components/order/` | OrderCard, OrderTimeline, OrderStatus, AddressCard |
| promotion | `components/promotion/` | CountdownTimer, FlashSaleBadge, BannerCarousel |

## 组件编写模式

```tsx
"use client";

import { Button as BaseButton } from "@base-ui/react/button";
import { forwardRef } from "react";
import { cva, type VariantProps } from "class-variance-authority";
import { cn } from "@mg/utils";

// 1. CVA 定义变体
const buttonVariants = cva("inline-flex items-center justify-center ...", {
  variants: {
    variant: { default: "bg-brand ...", destructive: "bg-error ..." },
    size: { sm: "h-8 px-3 text-sm", md: "h-10 px-4", lg: "h-12 px-6 text-lg" },
  },
  defaultVariants: { variant: "default", size: "md" },
});

// 2. Props = Base UI Props + CVA Variants
type ButtonProps = BaseButton.Props &
  VariantProps<typeof buttonVariants> & { asChild?: boolean };

// 3. forwardRef 封装
const Button = forwardRef<HTMLButtonElement, ButtonProps>(
  ({ className, variant, size, ...props }, ref) => (
    <BaseButton
      ref={ref}
      className={cn(buttonVariants({ variant, size }), className)}
      {...props}
    />
  ),
);
Button.displayName = "Button";

export { Button, buttonVariants };
export type { ButtonProps };
```

## 关键规则

- 每个组件文件顶部加 `"use client"` 指令
- 使用 `@base-ui/react` 的无头组件作为底座，用 CVA + Tailwind 类加样式
- 使用 `cn()` (来自 `@mg/utils`) 合并 className
- 所有组件用 `forwardRef` 暴露 ref
- 复合组件用 Compound 模式导出（如 `Dialog.Root`, `Dialog.Trigger`）
- 动画使用 Tailwind `transition-*` + Base UI 的 `data-[starting-style]` / `data-[ending-style]` 属性，不用 CSS keyframe `animate-*`
- 语义色优先：使用 `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `border-border` 等语义 token，不直接用 `blue-600`

## 导出结构

```
packages/ui/src/
├── index.ts                    # 汇总导出
├── components/
│   ├── general/
│   │   ├── index.ts            # 该类别所有组件 re-export
│   │   ├── button.tsx
│   │   └── ...
│   └── ...
└── shims/                      # ESM shim（勿动）
    ├── use-sync-external-store-shim.ts
    └── use-sync-external-store-with-selector.ts
```
